  "notes": "Executable local-runtime parity for orderCustomerSet and orderCustomerRemove error-path fidelity. Replay creates customer, order, B2B contact, and cancelled-order state through supported local mutations, then verifies happy set/remove, unknown order, unknown customer, B2B customer-not-permitted, and cancelled-order remove userErrors with no upstream calls."
